	<summary>
	3/24/1994--Introduced.
Amends Federal monetary law to require that all recurring Federal payments shall be paid by electronic funds transfer, according to regulations prescribed by the Secretary of the Treasury (except with respect to the Congress). Prescribes procedural guidelines for such transfers.

	</summary>
